the title of so soueraine honour vnto such kinde of Sacrifice? Though it be our duetie, and also healthful for vs, to offer vp the sacrifice of praise, and thankes: yet who euer called it hostiam salutarem, the healthful hoste? The sacrifice of praise here I meane, as it is our owne spiritual worke, for otherwise I confesse, the blessed Sacrifice it selfe of the body and bloude of Christe, is also not seldom named the sacrifice of praise, as your selfe haue in this Diuision alleged a place out of S. Basils Masse, where it is so called.
